                  <additions><!--THIS element in domlib CONTAINS ESCAPED HTML, thus it is not possible to reliably extract the information about pages. Please watch out.-->
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#1va">Fols. 1va-2</locus>vb: Unidentified hymn in praise of God and other saints.<q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 1va: በዘዚአሁ፡ አርአያወ፡ አምሳል፡ ይትአኰት፡ ወይሴባሕ፡ ስሙ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡…</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           Wälättä Mikaʾel mentioned in the supplication formula at the end of the text was probably linked to the first owner of the Ms. (?) Wäldä Śǝllase (s. Additio 3 and the supplication on fol. 35ra-rb).
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#31va">Fol. 31va</locus>: Note listing the names: King Yoḥannǝs (r. 1872-89), Metropolitan ʾAtnatewos (in tenure 1869-76), śätätot (?) Giyorgis, priest (qäsis) Fasilädäs, and qes gäbäz Kidanä Maryam.<q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 31va: ንጉሥነ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ጳጳስነ፡ አትና፡ ቴዎስ፡ ሠተቶት፡ ጊዎርጊስ[sic]፡ ወለቀሲ[ስ]ሒ፡ ፋሲለደስ፡ ወለ{ቄስ}፡ ገበዝሒ፡ ኪዳነ፡ ማርያም፡</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           Written in the same hand as that of the note written on fol. 1r (s. Varia). It is unclear why the names were listed.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#31va">Fol. 31va</locus>-vb: Ownership note.<q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 31va: ለዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘተሣየጦ፡ በወርቁ፡ ወልደ፡ ሠላሴ፡ ወብእሲቱ፡ ፍሥሐ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ወወለቱ፡ ወለተ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ከመ፡ ይኵኖሙ፡ መርሐ፡ በመንግሥተ፡ ሰማያት፡ ዘሠረቆ፡ ወዘፈሐቆ፡ በሥልጣነ፡ ጴጥሮስ፡ ወጳውሎስ፡ ውጉዘ፡ [fol. 31vb] ለይኵን።</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note mentions the Ms. was bought by Wäldä Śǝllase (his wife is Fǝśśǝḥa Giyorgis, his daughter is Wälättä Mikaʾel).
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a4">
                           <locus target="#31vb">Fol. 31vb</locus>: Ownership note.<q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 31vb: ለዘቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘተሳየጦ፡ ገብረ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ወለተ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ገብረ፡ አምላክ፡ ወለተ፡ መድኅን። ወለደ፡ አናንያ፡ ኪዳነ፡ ማርያም።</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note mentions that Gäbrä ʾƎgziʾabǝḥer and other individuals bought the Ms.
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Short note ገብረ፡ ጊዎርጊስ፡ ወለዲያቆንሒ written in the same hand that of Additio 2: fol. 1r.&#xD;
- Doodles: fol. 35v.</item>
